casebody.data:
HAMILTON, alias HAYDEN, v. SUPERIOR COURT OF CALIFORNIA, IN AND FOR MARIN COUNTY. No. 105,

Misc.

Decided October 9, 1961. Appellant pro se. Richard Gladstein and Norman Leonard for appellee. Per Curiam.

The motion to dismiss is granted and the appeal is dismissed. Treating the papers whereon the appeal was taken as a petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari is denied.
